      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN KADE (4) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at this track. Better than latest and can atone here. FANTANNA'S DREAM (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (19.97) last time in a Grade 5 at Bulli. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Can figure in the finish. BROOKLYN BRUTE (5) struggled in tougher grade last start after settling well back at Wentworth Park, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at this track (23.02) beating Ultra Violet in a Grade 5 on October 1. Can measure up this time. NO SHAME (8) jumps at a shorter trip and still warrants respect.",
